snippet.title: Best VGM 1143 - Mighty Switch Force! - Whoa I'm in Space Cuba
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1982 - https://youtu.be/VMt6f3DvTaU

Buy the OST @ http://virt.bandcamp.com/album/mighty-switch-force-ost

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

3DS
Mighty Switch Force! (2011)
Whoa I'm in Space Cuba
Jake Kaufman
